+Addressed in `src/policy/preview.py`. The fallback payload now preserves `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` instead of dropping them when `preview_enabled=False`.
+
+`T-214-02`  
+Classified as duplicate of `T-214-01`. No separate code change was applied because it reports the same reopened fallback regression.
